summary: An ordinance relating to zoning and providing for the rezoning of the east 104.66 feet of Lot 17 and east 104.66 feet of the south 1/2 of Lot 18, all in Block 5, Cedar Park Addition; with respect to Use and Area Districts, and amending Ordinance No. 45382, as amended, by adding thereto two new sections numbered 2-369 and 17-281, respectively.
